                     \\ SIMPLE JAVASCRIPT MAC DETECTION \\

Depending on your situation, you might need to handle things differently. Here are 3 methods
to detect mac in order to provide mac users with alternate content. They range from the
extra super gangster way of doing it, to the not-so-gangster way.
